WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.031 --> 00:00:10.011
 *Music* 

00:00:10.011 --> 00:00:13.059
 If you have your personal, legal, electronic signature 

00:00:13.059 --> 00:00:17.000
 on your phone, you will now learn how to do it. 

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.035
 You have the option of using your mobile phone signature with an existing Citizen Card 

00:00:22.035 --> 00:00:28.019
 via your existing financial online access or through a registry. 

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:31.060
 New is the possibility of online self-activation. 

00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:37.032
 In the new and easy online self-activation at www.SendStation.at, 

00:00:37.032 --> 00:00:42.043
 You need an online banking account and your mobile phone ready to receive. 

00:00:42.043 --> 00:00:46.020
 Enter your details and follow the instructions on the screen. 

00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:50.043
 You will receive a one-time code via SMS to check the mobile phone number. 

00:00:50.043 --> 00:00:53.064
 Then you will be redirected to your online bank account, 

00:00:53.064 --> 00:00:56.003
 to make a transfer. 

00:00:56.003 --> 00:01:01.088
 So your data will be checked and you will shortly receive a letter with the activation data. 

00:01:01.088 --> 00:01:08.095
 If you activate via FinanzOnline you need valid access to FinanzOnline, 

00:01:08.095 --> 00:01:12.012
 Participant and user identification and PIN. 

00:01:12.012 --> 00:01:16.099
 Log in and then start registering the cell phone signature. 

00:01:16.099 --> 00:01:22.031
 Upon completion, within a few days, you will receive an activation code that will help you 

00:01:22.031 --> 00:01:25.031
 complete the activation of the mobile phone signature. 

00:01:25.031 --> 00:01:30.068
 When activated with an active Citizen Card, which may be on your e-card, for example, 

00:01:30.068 --> 00:01:36.095
 you need an already activated citizen card, an operational card reader 

00:01:36.095 --> 00:01:41.048
 and your mobile phone ready to receive. 

00:01:41.048 --> 00:01:45.079
 Select "with citizen card" and follow the instructions. 

00:01:45.079 --> 00:01:51.004
 After completing the process, your mobile signature will be ready to use. 

00:01:51.004 --> 00:01:54.087
 If you prefer the personal way, you can use the cell phone signature 

00:01:54.087 --> 00:01:57.048
 be activated by a registration office. 

00:01:57.048 --> 00:02:03.043
 Registration offices are, for example, tax offices, the municipal office or a social insurance office. 

00:02:03.043 --> 00:02:07.051
 You will need an official photo ID and your mobile phone. 

00:02:07.051 --> 00:02:11.068
 The registry will do the activation for you free of charge 

00:02:11.068 --> 00:02:14.063
 and you can immediately use the cell phone signature. 

00:02:14.063 --> 00:02:22.040
 Find the nearest registration office near you at www.handy-signatur.at. 

